{"tid":1630422,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"連登越黎越多風，請自帶批判性思考","createTime":"2019-10-06T12:26:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T14:25:45.000Z","uid":76735,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5d69adfa343226fe33b931910eeb0219bbaf8994","tid":1630422,"uid":76735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:26:43.000Z","msg":"由十月一開始連登已經好多風吹黎吹去<br />\n由於好多示威者都係年輕人一輩 好易受影響<br />\n請睇連登時 自帶批判性思考諗下 咩應該做咩唔應該做<br />\n<br />\n有風吹 係藍店就裝修 唔裝修就對唔住我地被捕既手足<br />\n請大家諗下 只係口講發表意見就裝修 咁我地同中共有咩分別？<br />\n講啲唔岩聽 批評你既野就走去拆人地舖頭<br />\n同維尼一聽到批評佢既野就上門拉人 炒家有咩分別<br />\n我地要追求民主社會同時 唔可以令人地失去自由<br />\n請大家唔好比仇恨 憤怒 蒙蔽雙眼，唔好將自己變做黃衛兵<br />\n你地最撚憎既TVB 天與地都話<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「因為喺呢度，每一個支持同追求獨立音樂嘅人，佢哋都代表住每一種獨立同自主嘅做人方法。呢啲並唔係唔和諧嘅表現，和諧唔係一百個人講同一番說話，和諧係一百個人有一百句唔同說話之餘，又互相尊重。」</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日仲有人走去挑老解機 入面仲一大班五毛吹風搞老解唔洗驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n老解射死你地係唔需要比任何解釋<br />\n全世界每一個國家 有人無故闖入軍營 射死都係唔需要解釋<br />\n你就去挑老解機 比人射死都唔會對國際戰線有幫助<br />\n黑警都未撚搞掂 大家唔好走去越級挑機<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n放核彈都唔割，但求大家唔好咁易比風吹到走去做傻事<br />\n我唔想見到有手足係比老解射死 白白斷送左條命<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"756da0ccbe2db4b5b7603e5a330a0d1b60987bf8","tid":1630422,"uid":303304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:27:51.000Z","msg":"大家知唔知道宜家外國人點諗勇武<br />\n勇武要大家backup 啊！<br />\n<br />\n正式宣布：文宣洗地開始［行動po求置頂］<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630198\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630198</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ab5d3656764ee16d1e8168e5b844160a67bda24e","tid":1630422,"uid":76735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:29:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">當然福建幫 政府 紅背景（國企）絕對可以拆<br />\n 撞手足 斬手足個啲仆街陷家剷要即刻私了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"01761a2cae2ba61c0a36a9836d6b9c8fdb60de2d","tid":1630422,"uid":76735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:32:56.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18438be0619cbf076e221221d31d2d871076a0c0","tid":1630422,"uid":25483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:35:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d20f38ce9e4fe783f298252f6155ddc3d2cf54cd","tid":1630422,"uid":261478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:41:41.000Z","msg":"不分化 不篤魁 不割𥱊<br />\n勇和一家 對準政權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b4ee0841d057bd0a1fff801ad93fd64dacb055b","tid":1630422,"uid":76735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:44:56.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22273cd78dabb657d620ca6540abc7020c3a41c6","tid":1630422,"uid":76735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:16:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"33edb618c0bdc064bbb06e963e36c2edf1a4338d","tid":1630422,"uid":53610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:22:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"149a88d40ab6e5ff368e5ff999e28d9f3c53b3f4","tid":1630422,"uid":76735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:11:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"398bd89587d33fc748f4171336268a75d07c69a5","tid":1630422,"uid":196673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:25:45.000Z","msg":"Agger <br />\n呢場運動最緊要係獨立思考"}]}